Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.60,0:00:03.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The curtain rises on a mysterious new era...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.47,0:00:05.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Monday 7:00 reasoning show.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.43,0:00:07.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Included in the high-priced wine is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.43,0:00:09.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An important and enigmatic message.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.27,0:00:10.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.89,0:00:12.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.98,0:00:15.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.36,0:02:08.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My my, if it isn't Shiratori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.57,0:02:10.47,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Welcome to my mountain retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.67,0:02:13.65,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Please enjoy yourself to your heart's content this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:13.67,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)}Honjou Murozou (42)\N{\fs10} Apparel Company President
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.27,0:02:17.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I should be saying that. It was very kind of you to have invited me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.77,0:02:19.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, what about Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.69,0:02:23.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here's Mouri with some "grand vin"!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.23,0:02:24.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.44,0:02:25.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.07,0:02:28.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not good to shake that wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.99,0:02:29.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.33,0:02:33.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There won't be enough time for the dregs to settle back out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.79,0:02:34.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dregs?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.79,0:02:40.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The tannins and the pigmentation agents that collect at\Nthe bottom of the bottle will make the wine taste bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.92,0:02:44.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heh, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.30,0:02:48.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,More importantly, I'm honored that you agreed to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:51.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Hirose{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} will be very pleased as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.81,0:02:54.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's an honor for me as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.10,0:02:56.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Considering he's the president of the national wine association...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.68,0:02:59.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the recipient of a prestigious French medal...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.65,0:03:03.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's an honor to be invited to participate in\NHirose{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}'s 70th birthday celebration.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.82,0:03:06.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.11,0:03:06.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.90,0:03:10.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you please explain to Mouri sensei\Nthe arrangements for this evening?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:15.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The truth is, I was thinking of asking Mouri sensei\Nif he would mind performing in a short skit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.45,0:03:17.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.37,0:03:18.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That will be no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.46,0:03:21.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.50,0:03:24.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see, this is the scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.26,0:03:27.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, are you sure this will be OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.30,0:03:28.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.38,0:03:30.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:34.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You hid it in the trunk of the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.89,0:03:36.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit is you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:38.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:41.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should have another line before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.98,0:03:43.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.31,0:03:44.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.44,0:03:45.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why does it have to be me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:51.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ropeway goes all the way up to the summit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.53,0:03:54.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a great view, so why don't you check it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.24,0:03:55.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:57.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.17,0:04:05.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you here when you weren't invited?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.09,0:04:07.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you come to pick a fight with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.09,0:04:09.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, Akamaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:15.18,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I heard that it was a magnum of 1959 Pétrus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:15.20,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(290,0)} Akamaru Gorou (50)\N{\fs12} Translator
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.39,0:04:19.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's the best quality product that you\Nwill probably drink in your entire life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.10,0:04:23.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you think you can appreciate the taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:27.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And yet, the other day, you weren't able to\Ndetect the unusual taste of that Neuf du Pape.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.49,0:04:32.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate, I feel sorry for Hirose{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.11,0:04:35.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What, with this being his long-awaited 70th birthday celebration.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.87,0:04:38.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought, I should have been the presenter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.66,0:04:39.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.04,0:04:43.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.09,0:04:52.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today will be a memorable day, when your true\Nabilities as a wine connoisseur will be revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.97,0:04:56.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be happy seeing you embarrassed before such a large crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.05,0:04:57.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:11.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.57,0:05:12.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.36,0:05:16.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't see anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.41,0:05:23.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were worried about where to conceal the body...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.71,0:05:26.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you hid the body in the trunk of the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.00,0:05:31.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, and then your wife, who wasn't aware of its presence...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.09,0:05:33.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Drove the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.81,0:05:42.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've underestimated me, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.35,0:05:45.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me, the great detective, Mouri Kogorou.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.77,0:05:47.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you move over a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.69,0:05:48.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.65,0:05:52.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're back awfully early.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.19,0:05:56.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The truth is, I wanted to spend more time looking...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.55,0:05:59.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} suddenly said he had a stomachache.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.92,0:06:15.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.22,0:06:17.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.76,0:06:19.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for something I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.18,0:06:22.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess it must be inside the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.02,0:06:25.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, what about—?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.81,0:06:27.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, just put it over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.98,0:06:32.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, do you happen to know what happened to that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:36.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The man in the mustard-colored suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.07,0:06:38.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were talking to him about something, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.66,0:06:42.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we were having a serious conversation, weren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.66,0:06:44.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he's already gone home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.33,0:06:45.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.46,0:06:59.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, I can't accuse you of being the culprit\Nbased solely on circumstantial evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.72,0:07:01.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see, er...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:02.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Material evidence."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.47,0:07:05.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Material evidence is required.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:10.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:11.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.40,0:07:14.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, when did you guys get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.40,0:07:15.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At 4 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.06,0:07:49.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.10,0:07:51.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I lost something...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.52,0:07:52.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.40,0:07:57.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This thing you lost wouldn't happen to be\Na hamster or something like that, would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.90,0:08:00.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you're thinking it might have slipped in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:02.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it. It's a ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.29,0:08:12.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The key requires a fingerprint comparison...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.83,0:08:15.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So no one except Honjou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} could have come in, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.17,0:08:17.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.63,0:08:20.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.39,0:08:25.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Koike{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:27.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about the preparations for the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.89,0:08:30.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could I ask you to find this boy's ball instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.35,0:08:35.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until then, why don't you watch TV or something up on the 2nd floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.07,0:08:39.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,KAMEN...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.19,0:08:41.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,YAIBA!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:48.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you like Yaiba, little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:50.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My grandson likes it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:53.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's just started kindergarten this year though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.33,0:08:54.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.92,0:09:00.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's useless. There's no way I can remember these long lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.38,0:09:02.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I asked you if this would be OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.30,0:09:07.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you ask Honda san if it's all\Nright for you to just do a regular speech?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.85,0:09:09.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:22.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:25.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did your stomachache get better?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.24,0:09:27.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.41,0:09:32.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gotta go to the restroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.04,0:09:33.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.17,0:09:37.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, Honjou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.63,0:09:41.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it all right if we convert Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s skit into a regular speech?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.55,0:09:44.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems he can't remember the lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:46.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.05,0:09:51.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, before that, may I have the privilege\Nof a few words with Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.59,0:10:28.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.22,0:10:32.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.56,0:10:35.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He must have concealed Akamaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} here temporarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.68,0:10:38.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And while I was going around searching inside the house...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.19,0:10:40.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He moved him somewhere else, in\Ncase he was unfortunately discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.32,0:10:43.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must be in a completely secure location.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.11,0:10:45.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The wine storeroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.83,0:11:00.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for coming such a long way, Hirose{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:02.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The gratitude is all mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:07.50,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,For hosting such a grand party on my behalf...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:11.14,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Honjou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, everyone—my sincere thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.44,0:11:11.19,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(210,0)} Hiroso Shinya (70)\N{\fs13} Wine Critic
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.47,0:11:13.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That person is today's guest of honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.68,0:11:17.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The president of the national wine association, Hirose Shinya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.48,0:11:20.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's the French medal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.94,0:11:28.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In celebration of Hirose sensei's 70th birthday and in hopes\Nthat he will continue to play an active role hereafter...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.82,0:11:29.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.86,0:11:31.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.00,0:11:40.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.04,0:11:44.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, please hurry up and memorize this copy of your speech!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.26,0:11:48.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.76,0:11:52.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's now savor the highest-quality Bordeaux\Nwines that I have chosen for this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.22,0:11:54.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our initial selection...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.18,0:11:59.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A 1985 Chateau Haut-Brion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.27,0:12:02.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that one expensive?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:06.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's more than 100,000 yen per bottle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.86,0:12:09.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oooh! I'm looking forward to that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.74,0:12:12.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The value of a wine shouldn't be judged solely by its cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.45,0:12:18.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please take one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.34,0:12:32.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It has a mellow but elegant character.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.30,0:12:35.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.39,0:12:38.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, it's not just the flavor of the wine...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.18,0:12:41.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's important to enjoy the aroma and the coloring as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.85,0:12:45.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next, we have a Chateau Mouton Rothschild.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.56,0:12:47.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This one is a 1982.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.98,0:12:51.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a pretty picture on the label.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.11,0:12:52.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's called "Etiquette."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.07,0:12:54.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Etiquette?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.28,0:12:56.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, for Mouton's etiquette...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.91,0:13:00.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Each year a different well-known painter or artist draws one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.66,0:13:03.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's famous for its artistic taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.87,0:13:07.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The etiquette for 1970 was drawn by Chagall.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.21,0:13:09.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.55,0:13:13.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a 1992 Chateau Le Pin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.72,0:13:17.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A 1986 Chateau Lafite Rothschild.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.22,0:13:21.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And a 1990 Chateau Margaux.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.15,0:13:27.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hirose{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.65,0:13:31.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so, congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.24,0:13:37.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell me about the incident that\Noccurred in Kusaka Shouhei's wine cellar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.28,0:13:41.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! If I hadn't been there, that might have gone unsolved, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.37,0:13:45.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei, excuse me for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.17,0:13:47.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, Honjou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.96,0:13:48.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.25,0:13:51.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen Akamaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.05,0:13:54.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akamaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.05,0:13:57.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A translator of French literature.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.26,0:13:59.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's also famous for being a wine critic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.97,0:14:01.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems he got here around 3 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.77,0:14:05.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would you know something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.56,0:14:08.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just happened to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.48,0:14:09.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.73,0:14:10.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.69,0:14:14.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's terribly sorry he couldn't come to your long-awaited celebration.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:17.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said to give you his regards, Hirose{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:20.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. In that case, it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.53,0:14:22.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, I have some preparations to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.42,0:14:30.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, about that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.05,0:14:32.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.05,0:14:33.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.96,0:14:34.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.80,0:14:37.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s stomach is bothering him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:39.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's probably been drinking too many cold beverages.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.97,0:14:45.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.94,0:14:50.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.77,0:14:52.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm fine, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.07,0:14:54.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.32,0:14:57.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Little boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.95,0:15:01.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was this your ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.95,0:15:04.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was in the corner of the parking lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:05.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:07.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.13,0:15:13.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For half a century...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.13,0:15:16.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It has been waiting patiently until it has come to us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.05,0:15:18.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A gem in a bottle...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.30,0:15:20.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.80,0:15:22.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A 1959...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.97,0:15:25.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A magnum bottle of Chateau Petrus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.93,0:15:28.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,1959!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.23,0:15:29.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And a magnum!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.40,0:15:34.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me offer this now to Hirose{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:37.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Honjou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.86,0:15:39.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This makes me extremely happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.28,0:15:45.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To tell the truth, this should have been\Nuncorked and decanted a few hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.95,0:15:51.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when it comes to a wine of this caliber, it should\Nbe fully enjoyable even if we uncork it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.05,0:15:58.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.30,0:16:02.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, it must have been from that time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.76,0:16:04.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.10,0:16:06.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was unintentionally careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.68,0:16:10.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.02,0:16:14.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After half a century, even if I pour it directly into the glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.82,0:16:17.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I contend that we will find it just as satisfactory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.44,0:16:19.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will that be OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.03,0:16:22.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wine should be treated like a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.99,0:16:27.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well now, sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.43,0:16:44.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.43,0:16:46.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The dregs have been mixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.93,0:16:49.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The flavor is off too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.10,0:16:51.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That shouldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.90,0:17:02.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,May I try also?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.03,0:17:03.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.16,0:17:05.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.95,0:17:10.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.83,0:17:14.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.00,0:17:16.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone must have shook it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.71,0:17:19.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone shook it? We're not amateurs here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:22.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps the temperature in the storeroom got too high.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.34,0:17:23.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's also impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:27.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The temperature in the storeroom is kept\Nperfectly regulated through computer control.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.35,0:17:30.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it's a mystery then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.03,0:17:42.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could this be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.61,0:17:44.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By some chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.86,0:17:50.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Akamaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} made fun of him over something,\NHonjou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} flew into a rage and killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.45,0:17:54.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He then hid Akamaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} in the wine barrel by the tennis court.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.46,0:17:56.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.46,0:17:58.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since I was loitering around...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.38,0:18:00.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to conceal it to a more secure location...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.67,0:18:03.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He moved the body from the tennis court into the wine storeroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.18,0:18:07.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.18,0:18:10.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akamaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who he thought was dead, regained consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:21.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he noticed the Petrus had been placed\Nupright so that the dregs would settle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.07,0:18:22.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pétrus...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:38.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This will teach you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.08,0:18:40.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honjou!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.25,0:18:45.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since Akamaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} hasn't yet made an appearance...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.97,0:18:47.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He may have lost consciousness again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.09,0:18:49.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or in the worst case...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.22,0:18:53.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can I get into the wine storeroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.31,0:18:56.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honjou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is the only one who can open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.27,0:18:59.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.23,0:19:05.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the heck could have happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.99,0:19:10.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The wine is suddenly making me drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.49,0:19:14.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:18.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the famous Sleeping Kogorou!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.21,0:19:22.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's Sleeping...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.71,0:19:26.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honjou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you've fallen into a trap, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.63,0:19:27.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.38,0:19:28.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.76,0:19:33.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone who is jealous of you, Honjou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},\Nmust have come to this party to embarrass you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.22,0:19:37.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They secretly snuck into your wine storeroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.10,0:19:39.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to ruin that wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.02,0:19:41.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.40,0:19:43.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That must be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.61,0:19:45.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.61,0:19:48.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, but that's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.36,0:19:51.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to get into the wine storeroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:54.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It makes a comparison with my fingerprint.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.12,0:19:58.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely the culprit is someone who's\Nfamiliar with your security system.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.25,0:20:05.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it's possible they might still be hiding in\Nthere, which is where the remaining wine is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:08.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.13,0:20:09.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We need to stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.26,0:20:11.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a sacrilege against the wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.39,0:20:13.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's all go to the storeroom together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.18,0:20:15.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no. I'll go by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.76,0:20:16.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.02,0:20:19.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't know what the culprit will do if you back them into a corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.10,0:20:24.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And when you encounter them, they might have a broken wine bottle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.44,0:20:25.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.15,0:20:27.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:27.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.11,0:20:28.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.90,0:20:29.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Save the wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.78,0:20:30.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry to the storeroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.95,0:20:31.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.99,0:20:37.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akamaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.16,0:20:38.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akamaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.16,0:20:40.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.79,0:20:41.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akamaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.54,0:20:44.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.29,0:20:45.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Call for an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.38,0:20:46.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.88,0:20:51.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What does this mean, Honjou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.09,0:20:54.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.76,0:20:55.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honjou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.89,0:20:57.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.44,0:21:05.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy was ridiculing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.15,0:21:08.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said I didn't have the proper refinement or quality of character.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.48,0:21:12.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that I didn't have the qualifications to call myself a wine lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.57,0:21:14.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honjou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.28,0:21:17.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you truly a wine lover?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.29,0:21:19.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.95,0:21:21.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.29,0:21:23.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A wine storeroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.00,0:21:26.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a sacred place for a wine lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.84,0:21:29.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For one to use it in order to conceal a crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.59,0:21:30.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's unreasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.18,0:21:38.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Happily, Akamaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.39,0:21:40.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the case was closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.18,0:21:43.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.73,0:21:46.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The true victim in this case might be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.86,0:21:51.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The thing whose taste was ruined when it got involved\Nin the dirty fighting between human beings...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.49,0:21:53.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That bottle of wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.41,0:23:21.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sweetness is very mellow...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.87,0:23:24.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as you would expect, a vintage wine is exceptional.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.00,0:23:28.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How much did that cost?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.87,0:23:31.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was 10,000 yen, but...
